  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Being 18 years of age or older

          -  Meet ICSD-3 diagnostic criteria for Insomnia as confirmed by the telephone
             administered Interview

          -  Acess to the Internet

          -  Written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Physiological Insomnia

          -  Serious psychiatric co-morbidity that requires alternative treatment including major
             depression disorder, anxiety disorder, substance dependence, bipolar affective
             disorder, psychotic illness

          -  Epilepsy (seizure disorder)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
